        "caption": "FIG 2.0 - WALL WASH",
        "body_text": "<p><strong>Wall Washing</strong> occurs when the fixture is placed slightly further from the wall, creating a smooth, even gradient. This hides imperfections and turns the wall into a glowing canvas.</p>",
